OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772831515
OL,3,CWoman who smuggled military-grade
OL,4,Cweapons and #500,000 of heroin jailed
OL,6,FA woman who smuggled military-grade
OL,7,Fweapons and around #500,000 of heroin
OL,8,Finto the UK in a Peugeot has been
OL,9,Fjailed for nine years, the National
OL,10,FCrime Agency (NCA) said.
OL,12,FKasha Sanderson was stopped at Dover
OL,13,Fon February 24 last year after
OL,14,Farriving on a ferry from Calais.
OL,16,FThe 40-year-old told officers that she
OL,17,Fhad been in Lyon, France, scattering
OL,18,Fashes, but a search of her Irish-
OL,19,Fregistered Peugeot 3008 SUV uncovered
OL,20,Ftwo custom-built hides in the
OL,21,Ffootwells, according to the NCA.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
