FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772831515
OL,3,CWoman who smuggled military-grade
OL,4,Cweapons and #500,000 of heroin jailed
OL,6,FInside were 13 weapons, including two
OL,7,FSkorpion sub machine guns, an Uzi sub
OL,8,Fmachine gun, a Glock handgun and nine
OL,9,Fconverted blank firing pistols, as
OL,10,Fwell as 289 rounds of ammunition.
OL,12,FOfficers also found five kilograms of
OL,13,Fheroin.
OL,15,FSanderson from Bristol told officers
OL,16,Funder questioning that she thought she
OL,17,Fwas smuggling cannabis, but later
OL,18,Fadmitted smuggling firearms,
OL,19,Fammunition and Class A drugs, the NCA
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
