OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772831515
OL,3,CWoman who smuggled military-grade
OL,4,Cweapons and #500,000 of heroin jailed
OL,6,FShe was sentenced at Canterbury Crown
OL,7,FCourt on Thursday.
OL,9,FNCA branch commander Rachel Bramley
OL,10,Fsaid: "These terrifying weapons and
OL,11,Fammunition are out of the hands of
OL,12,Fextremely dangerous criminals.
OL,14,F"Firearms crime in the UK is among the
OL,15,Flowest in the world, but these guns
OL,16,Fhad the potential to cause horrific
OL,17,Fdamage.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
