OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772831515
OL,3,CWoman who smuggled military-grade
OL,4,Cweapons and #500,000 of heroin jailed
OL,6,F"We have seen in recent years the
OL,7,Ftragic consequences of entirely
OL,8,Finnocent victims getting caught in the
OL,9,Fcrossfire of criminals with automatic
OL,10,Fweapons such as Skorpion machine
OL,11,Fpistols.
OL,13,F"With Sanderson's jailing, the
OL,14,Forganised crime group behind this
OL,15,Fsmuggling plot have lost a trusted
OL,16,Fcourier and profits they are unable to
OL,17,Fplough back into further offences."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/4
